id: pm-5v5w
title: Implement CLI telemetry consent and runtime pipeline
description: Extend telemetry rollout with local OTEL collection path in pm CLI and re-verify all remote observability sources plus Grafana display evidence.
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: cli,gdpr,pm-cli,telemetry
created_at: "2026-04-25T21:33:00.979Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-25T22:42:11.715Z"
deadline: "2026-05-05T21:33:00.979Z"
author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 540
acceptance_criteria: "CLI emits redacted command telemetry and optional local OTLP spans, and the remote observability stack (RabbitMQ, Postgres, Prometheus, Loki, Tempo, Alloy, Grafana) shows live ingestion evidence."
parent: pm-lnq3
resolution: Added optional OTLP local span export in CLI telemetry runtime and validated complete remote observability ingestion path.
expected_result: CLI can emit command telemetry to ingestion endpoint and optional local OTLP collectors while Grafana data sources show live data from all stack components.
actual_result: Telemetry runtime now emits optional OTLP local spans with environment-based controls; local smoke and remote verification confirmed RabbitMQ/Postgres/Prometheus/Loki/Tempo/Alloy ingestion and Grafana data source/dashboard visibility.
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T22:41:57.248Z",codex-agent,"Follow-up implementation + verification: added optional local OTLP span export in src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts (uses OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_TRACES_ENDPOINT or OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT with /v1/traces auto-append, OTEL_SERVICE_NAME override, PM_TELEMETRY_OTEL_DISABLED kill-switch) and covered with tests/unit/telemetry-runtime.spec.ts. Local OTEL smoke check passed with embedded collector (request_count=2, span_names=pm.command.init + pm.command.list-open). Remote stack verification after fresh CLI commands (list-open/context): Postgres telemetry_events 825->829, RabbitMQ publish/deliver_get 826->830 with queue drained (messages_ready=0), Prometheus pm_telemetry_ingested_events_total 803->807, Tempo tempo_distributor_spans_received_total 3873->3929, Alloy exporter_sent_spans_ratio_total=3929 + loki_source_docker_target_entries_total non-zero, Loki query returned recent POST /v1/events 200 lines. Grafana verification: datasources listed (Prometheus, Loki, Tempo, Telemetry Postgres), health OK for Prometheus/Loki/Postgres, and Grafana proxy/ds-query calls returned live data for Prometheus metrics, Loki logs, Tempo trace search, and Postgres telemetry_events count; provisioned dashboard uid pm-cli-telemetry-overview present with telemetry panels backed by those datasources."
